  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      After one year neuroleptic maintenance treatment in patients with first episode
      schizophrenia, neuroleptic treatment will be continued vs. stepwise discontinued (randomized
      design) over a period of 1 year. Under both conditions prodrome based early intervention take
      place.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      After one year neuroleptic maintenance treatment in patients with first episode
      schizophrenia, neuroleptic treatment will be continued vs. stepwise discontinued (randomized
      design) over a period of 1 year. Under both conditions pharmacologic early intervention
      strategies in case of early sign of relapse will be applied.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
