  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients after 1 year of maintenance treatment after their first-episode in
             schizophrenia (according ICD-10 F20)

          -  Age between 18 and 55

          -  Informed consent

          -  One year neuroleptic maintenance treatment

          -  Reaching stable course

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Residence outside of the catchment area

          -  Legal reasons

          -  Insufficient knowledge of the german language

          -  Substance abuse or addiction

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Serious physical illness

          -  Organic brain disease

          -  Contraindication to neuroleptic treatment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
